# 1.3.6.1.4.1.29423.1021.3.1
#                  |	|  |
#      2V OID      |	|  |
# <--------------->|	|  |--> incremental value
#		   |<-->|
#		   |	|
#                  |	|--> object type: 1,2,3,4,5,9,11 *
#		   | 
#		   |--> ldap OID (default 1021) 
#
# Object type legenda: *
# - LDAP syntaxes = 1
